Recommendations:
We recommended that the Local Chief Executive:
Direct the full implementation of the provisions of RA No. 9003, together with the members of the Municipal Solid Waste Management Board, in order to avoid administrative sanctions mentioned therein;
Direct the persons responsible to submit the Ten Year Ecological SWMP to the NSWMC for approval;
Direct the MPDO to include in the proposal for the 20% DF the construction or rehabilitation of sanitary landfills, materials recovery facilities and purchase of related equipment; and
