The LSB to appropriate and disburse the SEF on PPAs that were cited in RA No. 5447 and RA No. 7160;
Persons responsible to ensure implementation of PPAs but strictly comply with the provisions of RA No. 9184;
The Municipal Budget Officer to coordinate with the LSB and re-appropriate the amounts set aside for the repair and rehabilitation of the district supervisor’s and principal’s office and all other PPAs that are not among those allowed by the above laws, rules and regulations; and
