Recommendations:
We recommended that the Municipal Treasurer shall:
See to it that collections on hand are deposited daily or not later than the next banking day;
Direct Collectors to turnover collections on hand at the close of each business day to the Designated Liquidating Officer;
Direct the responsible persons to observe issuance of pre-numbered official receipts in strict numerical sequence;
Issue letter of authority to the Barangay Treasurer as deputized collector and request prompt turnover of collections to the Designated Liquidating Officer.
